📌 Why This Approach?

✔ Manually maps DTO ↔ Model without using external libraries.
✔ Ensures null safety to avoid NullPointerException.
✔ Uses List<> mappings for nested objects (NameDetails, AddressDetails, etc.).
✔ Can be extended easily for additional fields or custom mapping logic.

